# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandip2.rpy:38
translate portuguese brandip2_11921a24:

    # pc "Don't sell yourself short."
    pc "Não te subestimes."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandip2.rpy:39
translate portuguese brandip2_b6b8ea7a:

    # pc "You also give really good head."
    pc "Também fazes um excelente sexo oral."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandip2.rpy:41
translate portuguese brandip2_8baa08dc:

    # fd "Haha! Yeah, I guess I'm pretty good at that too."
    fd "Haha! Sim, acho que também sou bastante boa nisso."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandip2.rpy:43
translate portuguese brandip2_885101cc:

    # fd "I'm really proud of what I've put together, but I always feel inferior when I talk to them about my work."
    fd "Tenho muito orgulho no que construí, mas sinto-me sempre inferior quando falo com eles sobre o meu trabalho."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/BrandiConversations/brandip2.rpy:44
translate portuguese brandip2_2d2bc8e2:

    # pc "You bring happiness to a lot of people. Hard to ask for more than that."
